[[File:NTS Area 2.png|thumb|150px|Area 2 within the [[Nevada Test Site]].]]
'''Area 2''' is a division of the [[Nevada Test Site]] in the [[Mojave Desert]]. The area is located 18 miles south-east of [[Area 51]].

Area 2 was the site of 144 tests comprising 169 detonations.<ref name="DOE/NV-209" /> Shot "Gabbs", intended for 1993, was abandoned in place.<ref name="DOE/NV-1212" />

